{
  "texts": [
    "Reinforcement learning is employed to train agents in dynamic environments, with rewards being offered for correct actions and punishments for errors.",
    "The following will present a number of illustrative examples of machine learning, demonstrating its considerable potential and the diversity of its applications.",
    "A clustering technique may be employed for the purpose of detecting instances of fraud.",
    "This is achieved by grouping transactions or data within a system based on a number of different dimensions and data attributes.",
    "The initial stage of the process is to cluster transactions or other data in order to group items with similar characteristics together."
  ]
}